data.text:
Description

As of December 10, 2018, a building permit has not been issued by the Kansas City Building Department. An architect has been identified. This project will go out to bid to an invited list of general contractors, but a timeline for bidding has not been established. Although a firm construction timeline was not disclosed, construction is not expected to begin prior to the second quarter of 2019.
